# Catalog Authenticity (Media-First)

Underground Archive is a curated cultural archive. **Authenticity > quantity.** Never generate fake content.

Curation workflow (reintroduction, ingestion, no mass cleanup): `.cursor/rules/catalog-curation-mode.mdc`.

## Scope

Catalog/data only: content, metadata, builders, generators, validation/ingestion scripts. **Never playback.**

## Public artist gate

Artist appears publicly only with at least one:

- verified playable Spotify track, OR
- verified YouTube set with **API-fetched duration ≥ 10 minutes**

## Tracks / releases / sets

- Tracks: valid Spotify track ID/URL only
- Releases: real Spotify album/release URL/ID only
- Sets: valid YouTube ID, playable, API duration ≥ 10 min — never invent/hardcode durations

## Delete (targeted only)

Placeholder/generated media, invalid URLs, album/artist URLs as tracks, fabricated metadata, sets under 10 min after API check.

Do **not** mass-remove artists during Curation Mode. Skip unverified candidates instead.
